{"text_id":128223,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigate"," the"," relationship"," between"," Is","ing"," spin"," glass"," models"," and"," Is","ing"," models"," at"," high"," temperature",","," providing"," a"," rigorous"," formulation"," and"," detailed"," proof"," for"," general"," graphs","."," The"," motivation"," for"," our"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," understand"," the"," behavior"," of"," spin"," glasses",","," a"," class"," of"," materials"," that"," exhibit"," a"," range"," of"," complex"," phenomena",","," including"," memory"," and"," rejuvenation"," effects",","," as"," well"," as"," aging",".","\n\n","To"," address"," this"," challenge",","," we"," develop"," a"," mapping"," between"," Is","ing"," spin"," glass"," models"," and"," Is","ing"," models"," at"," high"," temperature",","," which"," allows"," us"," to"," analyze"," the"," former"," using"," the"," well","-","established"," techniques"," of"," the"," latter","."," Our"," approach"," is"," based"," on"," a"," high","-","temperature"," expansion",","," which"," we"," show"," to"," be"," convergent"," and"," to"," provide"," an"," effective"," means"," of"," approximating"," the"," partition"," function"," of"," the"," spin"," glass"," model",".","\n\n","The"," key"," result"," of"," our"," work"," is"," a"," rigorous"," proof"," of"," the"," mapping"," for"," general"," graphs",","," which"," extends"," previous"," research"," that"," had"," focused"," on"," specific"," graph"," structures","."," This"," proof"," relies"," on"," a"," combination"," of"," combinatorial"," and"," probabilistic"," techniques",","," including"," the"," use"," of"," coupling"," arguments"," and"," the"," F","KG"," inequality",".","\n\n","Our"," research"," provides"," a"," theoretical"," foundation"," for"," the"," study"," of"," spin"," glasses",","," which"," has"," implications"," for"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," fields",","," including"," condensed"," matter"," physics",","," computer"," science",","," and"," statistical"," mechanics","."," By"," establishing"," a"," rigorous"," mapping"," between"," Is","ing"," spin"," glass"," models"," and"," Is","ing"," models"," at"," high"," temperature",","," we"," provide"," a"," powerful"," tool"," for"," understanding"," the"," behavior"," of"," these"," complex"," materials",","," and"," pave"," the"," way"," for"," future"," research"," in"," this"," area","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}